    <h1>Social Network</h1>
    <p>
        A social network is a digital platform that allows people to <br />
        connect, communicate, and share content in real time. <br />
        These networks have transformed the way we interact, <br />
        creating virtual communities that transcend geographical boundaries. <br />
        From personal use to commercial purposes.
    </p>
